  "title": "Sri Lanka imposes price controls on rice",
  "body_lines": [
    "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Sri Lanka\u2019s Consumer Affairs Authority has imposed price controls on rice after a earlier removing them when the controls triggered shortages.",
    "The CAA has decreed that Nadu variety steamed rice should be sold at 220 rupees."
